text: Gorny () is a rural locality (a village) in Kushnarenkovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 6 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Kushnarenkovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Gorny, Kushnarenkovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
